	+ A unique, always-on display that provides essential information, such as time, date, and notifications, without waking the device.

**Colors:**

* The Aurum will be available in four stunning color options:
	+ Aurum (a luxurious, gold-inspired finish).
	+ Midnight Blue (a deep, rich blue hue).
	+ Cosmic Black (a sleek, space-inspired design).
	+ Rose Gold (a elegant, rose-gold finish).

**Pricing:**

* The Aurum will be priced competitively, starting at $999 for the base model (8GB RAM, 128GB storage).
* The top-of-the-line model (16GB RAM, 512GB storage) will retail for $1,299.

